title: Blake Shelton coming to KFC Yum! Center in 2016
text:
Country superstar Blake Shelton, who seems to make more headlines for divorces and girlfriends than for music, will perform Feb. 19 at the KFC Yum! Center.
Tickets go on sale Oct. 23 at 10 a.m. at www.LiveNation.com , all Ticketmaster outlets, the KFC Yum! Center box office and by phone at 800-745-3000.
Shelton has had a string of Top 5 hits since 2012, including this year's "Sangria." His biggest song is "Boys Round Here," which helped start the bro-country movement, and you can check that out below.
Reporter Jeffrey Lee Puckett can be reached at (502) 582-4160 and jpuckett@courier-journal.com.
